12.short_description: TECNOTIFERET is a company provides development in technology for the processing of electronic waste.

18.description:
80 million tons of E-waste worldwide have no proper means of disposal. 30% of this waste is plastic, which can be reincorporated to a useful lifecycle reduce the need for new resources. The worldwide E-recycling market has been calculated to be over $6.8 billion USD. 

Tecnotiferet has developed a working mobile recycling plant that processes E-Waste. This proprietary technology accurately processes plastics and obtains a product with a relatively high market value. 

Tecnotiferet has a highly professional team supported by qualified recycling advisors in the market and proposes an innovative business model, providing alternative solutions to a Global problem. 

We are currently looking for strategic partners to scale up our company and help our mission of becoming a relevant player in tackling waste problems globally. 

Tecnotiferet is a mobile recycling plant built to solve the e-waste problem. It can be placed close to the supply, saving the logistics costs as it processes high value engineering plastics contained in E-Scrap.
